comment: Four men and women in blue aprons strand in front of a table where there are many white plates and small blue bowls .
A tattooed girl , with strands of blue hair , draws stem-like art on a wall .
A baby is playing with a strand of beads .
A man hangs on to a strand of cloth with his big toe , his fingers and his teeth while standing on a platform by a river .
A rock climber wearing a Santa suit is hanging from a strand of Christmas lights .
A man touching a hanging strand of lamps .
A man in a blue striped shirt strands next to a woman .
People standing on top of a stranded boat .
A woman in a dark green tank top holds a long strand of another woman 's red-colored hair while running a hairbrush through it .
A young girl is stranded in front of a large rock in the middle of a river .
A group of workers stand over strands of marigolds at a marketplace .
A man in a plaid jacket is cutting fabric with several colorful strands of fabric behind him .
